    "Accordingly, we investigate an approach intended to measure and control what seems to be a desirable function in LLMs intended to facilitate human creativity.",
    "First, adopting the socialcognitive theory of Bandura (2001), we develop a framework of four features through which Agency may be expressed -Intentionality, Motivation, Self-Efficacy, and Self-Regulation.",
    "For each feature, we differentiate between how strongly or weakly it is expressed in a dialogue (Section 3).",
    "As a testbed, we choose a collaborative task that involves discussing the interior design of a room (Section 4), and collect a prototype dataset of 83 English human-human collaborative interior design conversations comprising 908 conversational snippets, annotated for Agency and its features on these conversational snippets (Section 5).",
    "1 We analyze this dataset to study the factors that contribute to high-and low-Agency and find that strong expressions of intentionality significantly impact Agency in conversations (Section 6)."
  ],
